@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ufdyot(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v2 + 0.81)
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = v2
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.exp((tmp + 0.06 * v1 + 0.65)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.66 - v1 + 0.77)) / (0.39 + wp.cos(v0 + 0.49)))
    data[tid] = v0
